        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-gray-200">We envision a world where education is lifelong, continuous, and accessible to all. Our goal is to provide personalized learning experiences that allow learners to expand their knowledge and skillset at any stage in their life, regardless of their location.</p>
