      <div class="point">
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-semibold text-white">2. Democratizing Education</h3>
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg text-gray-200">Our mission is to break down barriers to education. By leveraging cutting-edge technology, we aim to provide equal access to world-class educational resources, enabling individuals to learn, grow, and succeed on their own terms.</p>
